{"tid":597081,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android廣告病毒偽裝成Wi-Fi服務　500萬部電話被感染","createTime":"2018-03-18T09:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T05:26:48.000Z","uid":1886,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"432368c36ea65d37ad88117294f9e7d7055a5ea7","tid":597081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:38:10.000Z","msg":"網絡安全公司 CheckPoint 安全研究員指出，自從 2016 年以來，一種稱為「RottenSys」的惡意廣告軟件，感染了 500 萬部 Android 流動裝置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，普遍在中國大陸境內發售，當中包括了 Honor、華為、小米、OPPO、Vivo、Meizu 等中國手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。研究員指這些病毒在手機銷售給買家之前已經被混入在手機之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，假扮成「Wi-Fi 服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，並在用家使用手機時顯示全頁廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n根據 CheckPoint 發表的報告，指「RottenSys」有害程式現時已感染接近 500 萬部 Android 流動裝置，在手機交到使用者之前，這些有害程式已經被預載於手機中。根據調查，在小米手機「紅米」系列中，發現一項名為「System Wi-Fi service」的應用程式，CheckPoint 工程師發現程式取得了與 Wi-Fi 服務完全無關的行事曆、背景下載，以及其他不必要的權限許可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nCheckPoint 指出，「RottenSys」有害程式為免被用戶發覺，在植入初期不會有太多活動，只是在背後與神秘伺服器連接，下載有害程式。之後程式會實行一個虛擬架構「Small」，在主畫面上，或者顯示彈出式視窗，顯示全頁廣告。據調查這些廣告是連結到中國騰訊的廣告平台「廣點通」以及百度的「Baidu AD Exchange」服務。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-03-17-17.28.41-768x193.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-03-17-17.28.41-768x193.png&h=ed8ec1fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲有害程式最初會通過細小框架，逐步下載有廣告顯示能力的有害程式</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/03/17/rottensys/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2Frottensys%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=XdPyjybqQaprp66llt%2BsRf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d2e47bce\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/03/17/rottensys/tech-secure/</a></div>"},{"pid":"5f200f7a9269d5998ad955ce528d2a8eb258f30e","tid":597081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:39:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Fig7-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2FFig7-1.png&h=db77bf53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經調查後，CheckPoint 發現有 49.2% 中了有害程式的 Android 裝置，是經由總部設在中國杭州的「天湃淺裝」「天湃面」流動電話代理商的販售渠道中購得。Honor、華為、小米、OPPO、Vivo、Meizu 等中國產手機受到感染。CheckPoint 指有害程式製作者在過去 10 日已經得到超過 130 萬次的廣告顯示次數，推則廣告收入達到 11.5 萬美元（約90萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-03-17-17.28.01-768x590.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-03-17-17.28.01-768x590.png&h=19e241a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲CheckPoint估算10日內有害程式已為製作者賺取 11 萬美元收入</span></div>"},{"pid":"8bbebc8dd3a44a4733ac6c4e294bcdbe4f74ad82","tid":597081,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">CheckPoint 指出以下 4 個 Package 以及 3 個 App 名稱同「RottenSys」有害程式有關，呼籲使用者如發現有這些程式或服務，便應盡早刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-03-17-17.27.18-768x255.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-03-17-17.27.18-768x255.png&h=4ca8f4f2&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"351bb98f69d181aaf561c2e0c5431a8c3163b489","tid":597081,"uid":13718,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:43:23.000Z","msg":"華爲班垃圾打手死出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19a7f4b2bc9d7eedb4367de44b85a3f436edacf","tid":597081,"uid":77143,"like":14,"dislike":19,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大力恥笑熱衷自由嘅An狗"},{"pid":"d982bc61de42acd47250ca95c71bf4fd04291e87","tid":597081,"uid":29314,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:45:57.000Z","msg":"用支那機都預左啦"},{"pid":"70b3eaa0522af554dc5e9f16670ab84e54f55d26","tid":597081,"uid":12994,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:56:57.000Z","msg":"其實 講真呀<br />\n用得大陸機 你話唔係貪平真係搵鬼信<br />\n我就當呢啲機真係勁過iphone又點<br />\n之後帶黎既問題 真係估唔到<br />\n呢啲大數據 你唔知佢拎到啲咩<br />\n而且你部機不斷 loading <br />\n真係唔知邊個先係傻<br />\n<br />\n點解大陸死都要用咁多錢 拉返google同apple返去<br />\n係因為資料姐<br />\n<br />\n不過實有人話我呢啲二打六唔驚比人偷<br />\n聚沙成塔呀傻系"},{"pid":"07fe85b398edc290fd32da7cb0838f58c77dba5d","tid":597081,"uid":52595,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7a265b7446036ab9a06bd159576753353e1736a","tid":597081,"uid":109383,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"呢個po 五毛退散<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95d97864541d2a0a8e4e5347f94de0fb0c41367","tid":597081,"uid":63,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:01:11.000Z","msg":"唔好睇得自己咁重要 <br />\n無人想要你d 資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p